1:18:20.460 --> 1:18:22.350
hasn't had a shag in some time.

1:18:22.550 --> 1:18:25.050
- Well, you knew my situation
when we were introduced, sir.

1:18:25.250 --> 1:18:26.880
<i>Let the tiles sit overnight.</i>

1:18:27.080 --> 1:18:28.930
You always said I had an eye.

1:18:29.130 --> 1:18:32.400
I think I've finally started
trusting it again.

1:18:33.970 --> 1:18:36.930
- Well, you painted a very
different picture of yourself.

1:18:37.130 --> 1:18:38.720
<i>You did, too.</i>

1:18:38.920 --> 1:18:41.720
You know,
I don't think I can live up

1:18:41.920 --> 1:18:43.680
to your hopes and dreams.

1:18:43.880 --> 1:18:45.410
It's too much.

1:18:50.900 --> 1:18:53.380
When you look at a painting
too long,

1:18:53.580 --> 1:18:55.780
you can stop seeing it.

1:18:55.980 --> 1:18:59.430
I think I've had the time
to focus again

1:18:59.630 --> 1:19:03.440
and I just
underestimated its value.

1:19:03.640 --> 1:19:05.090
<i>- ...or pink for</i>
<i>the pitchers of water.</i>

1:19:05.290 --> 1:19:07.880
<i>- You're supposed to be</i>
<i>with your family.</i>

1:19:08.080 --> 1:19:10.880
And this is just a mistake.

1:19:11.080 --> 1:19:14.610
I just wish that I could see it
a little bit earlier.

1:19:20.190 --> 1:19:21.800
<i>- ...our shine off of</i>
<i>our beautiful metallic tile...</i>

1:19:22.000 --> 1:19:23.460
That's it, then?

1:19:23.660 --> 1:19:25.710
<i>- Now it's time</i>
<i>to start grouting.</i>

1:19:28.540 --> 1:19:31.410
Yeah. That's it.

1:19:34.330 --> 1:19:36.910
<i>- ...into the cracks until</i>
<i>it is in there nice and tight.</i>

1:19:37.110 --> 1:19:39.560
Look, take care, Mr. Marlowe.

1:19:39.760 --> 1:19:41.780
<i>- After about 30 minutes,</i>
<i>it'll start drying...</i>

1:19:41.980 --> 1:19:44.000
You too.

1:19:44.200 --> 1:19:45.910
Take care.

1:19:56.570 --> 1:19:58.800
I'll turn off my phone now.

1:19:59.000 --> 1:20:00.890
Great.

1:20:01.090 --> 1:20:04.190
<i>- Now we get to do</i>
<i>our first full piece.</i>

1:20:04.390 --> 1:20:06.930
<i>Uninhibited, no weird cuts,</i>
<i>so...</i>

1:20:17.290 --> 1:20:18.990
Hey.

1:20:19.190 --> 1:20:20.330
Hey.

1:20:23.680 --> 1:20:26.770
You know, I made this for you.

1:20:34.520 --> 1:20:38.650
I think the same of you.

1:20:52.580 --> 1:20:54.710
Let's dance.

1:20:56.320 --> 1:20:58.020
Okay.

1:21:11.470 --> 1:21:13.390
Hey.

1:21:16.340 --> 1:21:20.870
♪

